Path: Nushell
Content:
@hustcer:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17659] Increased help indention to fix the docs build error (#17659)
@fdncred:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17655] Updated 
``entry``
 to 
``repl_entry``
 for better understanding (#17655)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17654] Updated nushell to latest reedline commit 4ad0d0cb (#17654)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17653] Normalized slashes for 
``which``
 output (#17653)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17643] Allowed 
``which``
 to show where the file resides (#17643)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17639] Added more standardization to command arguments (#17639)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17635] Allowed 
``view source``
 to store file location in metadata (#17635)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17627] Fixed 
``detect columns``
 panic with unicode chars (#17627)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17610] Added custom subcommand help (#17610)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17596] Fixed 
``let``
 and ensured glob variables expand correctly in runtime and tests (#17596)
@NotTheDr01ds:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17645] Fixed 
``history | last 10``
 being in descending order (#17645)
@pickx:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17637] Fixed view span to allow zero-length spans and reject out-of-bounds spans (#17637)
@Juhan280:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17626] Fixed compilation on targets other than linux, windows and macos (#17626)
@fmotalleb:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17624] Fixed android builds (#17624)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17619] Fixed android builds failing with arboard clipboard (#17619)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17616] Added 
``clip``
 config (#17616)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17572] Added native clipboard support using arboard (#17572)
@Bahex:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17617] Refactored par-each to reduce object churn by reusing closures (#17617)
@amaanq:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17613] Fixed using 
``writeln!``
 instead of 
``format!``
 and 
``write_all``
 (#17613)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17606] Fixed replacing eprintln! with writeln! in error reporting to prevent double-panic (#17606)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17580] Fixed ls to escape control characters in filenames to prevent terminal corruption (#17580)
@veeceey:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17607] Stripped ANSI escape codes from custom completion values (#17607)
@teddygood:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17600] Fixed ParseOption handling in from ini (#17600)
@blindFS:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17598] Added cellpath completion fallback to type based when value is unknown (#17598)
@astral-l:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17595] Added 
``--timeout``
 flag to 
``input listen``
 (#17595)
@132ikl:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17579] Made 
``collect``
 a keyword command and checked pipefail on 
``Instruction::Collect``
 (#17579)
@monigarr:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17546] Added PR 10 (of 10) Issue 5066 help text nu command network system viewers (#17546)
@app/dependabot:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17585] Bumped rmcp from 0.14.0 to 0.16.0 (#17585)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17584] Bumped quickcheck from 1.0.3 to 1.1.0 (#17584)
